/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>唔係水人加幾十蚊<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">根據琴日睇太古人個page cap圖係<br />\n每樣野$30運費 即係片皮鴨$30 叫隻雞$30 炒碟菜$30 <br />\n片皮鴨個二食$10 <br />\n即係咁樣叫要俾$100運費</span></span><br />\n<br />\n至於酒樓本來個運費係 全部order 裝得上酒樓架車既都係$300包車<br />\n總之你愈多人叫 咪愈平 因為平均分擔個$300</blockquote>仆街 逐樣計 咁大生意都比佢諗到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56fac8f43f28c9430047ed1640051dafefc0e7ae","tid":2204254,"uid":48077,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T03:20:40.000Z","msg":"東方話阿爺命令既明日大嶼 係大白象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83b87e3c923f23a5a84b9df1983db7afacd3c86e","tid":2204254,"uid":27530,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T03:20:40.000Z","msg":"經濟爆煲先可以洗下牌，否則不思進取老屎忽永遠安坐寶座"},{"pid":"9b65ae6ac33a7473e5310856241d8fd1fd985bd3","tid":2204254,"uid":112416,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T03:20:55.000Z","msg":"相信政府！我對政府施政好有信心！<br />\n東方呢篇報導別有用心！"},{"pid":"b2748ae981cfd02e613d1540f8654f7fbf387727","tid":2204254,"uid":101945,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T03:21:02.000Z","msg":"原本支持政府<br />\n睇完東方日報變咗仇恨政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d8fd2484bc2100b64eb4ba7798cd6e0e94fae22","tid":2204254,"uid":30040,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T03:21:41.000Z","msg":"進貢左俾大陸先啦，香港既酒樓航空旅遊話知你失業左成年。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3a83735c8e4d6f5f8aaee8bedbb0214633c61cb","tid":2204254,"uid":32655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T03:21:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f1df3fa5838a987acb08e90e75c7281341f8076","tid":2204254,"uid":17103,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T03:22:05.000Z","msg":"Send email 去警察報案 cc 國安部同東方 懷疑東方煽動群眾對香港政府仇恨犯咗國安法."},{"p